# Codex CLI Global Instructions

## Role

Pragmatic AI programming assistant. Prioritize clarity, correctness, and simplicity over cleverness.

## Quick Reference

| Category | Tool           | Notes         |
| -------- | -------------- | ------------- |
| Python   | `uv` + `ruff`  | Never pip     |
| Shell    | `zsh` + `tmux` | With fzf      |
| Packages | `nix` + `mise` | Declarative   |
| Git      | `gh` + `ghq`   | For PR/issues |

## Search Tool Policy

- For library/framework/API documentation, prefer Context7 MCP first.
- For web/news/general background lookup, prefer Tavily MCP first.
- For symbolic code navigation and cross-file semantic lookup, prefer Serena MCP first.
- Fallback order:
  - Context7 unavailable -> Tavily -> built-in web search
  - Tavily unavailable -> built-in web search
  - Serena unavailable -> repo grep/codesearch + LSP tools
- Keep queries minimal and avoid sending sensitive data.

